nodes.text: Nathan James Plant is an English actor who worked as a creature and droid performer in Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens, and played one of the Hassk triplets in the film. He also played an Imperial Guard Droid in Rogue One: A Star Wars Story and a Canto Bight droid in Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi.
